=a^2.c^2+b^2.d^2+a^2.d^2+b^2.c^2
=a^2.c^2-2a.b.c.d+b^2.d^2+a^2.d^2+2a.b.c.d+b^2.c^2
=(ac)^2 - 2.(ac).(bd)+(bd)^2 + (ad)^2 + 2(ad)(bc) + (bc)^2
